{"sections":{"main":{"type":"page-about","settings":{}},"page_heading_g9PJyw":{"type":"page-heading","blocks":{"1_tpzFAb":{"type":"1","settings":{"page_title":"About Us","text_cl":"#111111","text_fs":36}}},"block_order":["1_tpzFAb"],"name":"Page heading","settings":{"layout":"container","background_heading_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","breadcrumb_color":"#111111","show_banner":false,"min_height":200,"parallax":false,"show_overlay":false,"overlay":54,"design":"text-overlay-image","text_postion":"text-center"}},"custom_html_3MepXw":{"type":"custom-html","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"About Us","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","content_html":"<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-43232f6b-7fff-f0a5-ee6e-20ae27edd9b8\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">With over a decade of experience, LEDSONE has grown from a small lighting supplier into a leader in modern, stylish lighting solutions across the UK and Europe. From our Coventry headquarters and additional warehouse in Germany, we’ve dedicated ourselves to bringing innovative and energy-efficient lighting options to homes and businesses alike, blending quality and affordability with excellent customer service.<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Our Mission<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Our journey started with a vision to illuminate spaces beautifully without compromising on sustainability or style. Over the years, we’ve learned what our customers value most – reliability, efficiency, and aesthetics. LEDSONE offers a curated selection of lighting products designed for those who want the best of form and function in their spaces. We don’t just sell lights; we help people transform their environments.<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Why LEDSONE?<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">The lighting market often presents a confusing choice: low-priced, low-quality products that don’t last, or overpriced designer pieces that don’t fit most budgets. At LEDSONE, we’ve created a middle ground, offering exclusive, high-quality lighting options without breaking the bank. Our range includes energy-efficient LEDs, modern chandeliers, and smart lighting options, each selected for style, performance, and affordability.<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">We aim to be more than just a lighting store. We bring a sense of joy to our customers by offering unique, futuristic designs that go beyond the standard, dull fixtures. LEDsOne products are crafted to make a statement and make lighting an exciting part of every room’s personality.<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Our Commitment to Quality<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Our range is carefully edited to include only the best from each category. Every product we offer is chosen for its quality, style, and durability. We don’t believe in selling hundreds of the same thing; instead, we choose the best of the best, delivering lighting that enhances every space. For us, it’s not just about lights – it’s about helping our customers experience the impact of well-chosen lighting on their daily lives.<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Our Product Range and Vision<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">We aim to offer our customers a variety of the latest lighting products, including lampshades, vintage lighting materials, cables, transformers, pendant lights, fancy lights, and accessories. With more than 10 years in the industry, we know exactly which direction to take to supply high-quality, budget-friendly, tailor-made products just for you. We offer all of this while providing excellent customer service and friendly support.<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">We keep a close eye on the latest trends in lighting products and put our customers’ wishes first. This focus is why we have satisfied customers throughout the UK and Europe and are proud to be part of the electrical industry. Most importantly, we believe shopping is a right, not a luxury, so we strive to deliver the best products at affordable prices, shipping them to you wherever you are located.<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">Our Customers’ Satisfaction<\/span><\/p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 12pt; margin-top: 12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">The interests of our customers are always our top priority. We hope you enjoy our products as much as we enjoy making them available to you anytime.<\/span><\/p>\n<div><span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><br><\/span><\/div><\/span>","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"de27bbae-8b57-4758-bfe7-5ac9b1179505":{"type":"custom-text","blocks":{"template--16584037925111__de27bbae-8b57-4758-bfe7-5ac9b1179505-1665713233cd3512b4-0":{"type":"sub_heading","settings":{"sub_heading":"<p>Why Choose Us<\/p>","sub_color":"#999999","sub_fs":12,"sub_fw":500,"sub_tf":"uppercase","sub_mt":0,"sub_mb":0}},"template--16584037925111__de27bbae-8b57-4758-bfe7-5ac9b1179505-1665713233cd3512b4-1":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Our Top Collections","heading_color":"#111111","heading_fs":40,"heading_fw":400,"heading_tf":"unset","heading_mt":0,"heading_mb":10}},"template--16584037925111__de27bbae-8b57-4758-bfe7-5ac9b1179505-1665713233cd3512