 each selected for style and performance. We bring joy to our customers with unique, futuristic designs that make lighting an exciting part of every room’s personality.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","txt_color":"","txt_fs":16,"txt_fw":400,"txt_tf":"unset","txt_mt":1,"txt_mb":15}},"template--16584037925111__26c21a87-4e2f-4f70-a443-ad63d4341ac2-16655668072faff6b4-2":{"type":"buttons","disabled":true,"settings":{"btn_content":"Learn More","button_type":"link","button_link":"","button_target":false,"b_mt":0,"b_mb":15}}},"block_order":["7037bd9d-7ccb-4b05-b7b9-0a3b718156b1","template--16584037925111__26c21a87-4e2f-4f70-a443-ad63d4341ac2-16655668072faff6b4-0","template--16584037925111__26c21a87-4e2f-4f70-a443-ad63d4341ac2-16655668072faff6b4-1","template--16584037925111__26c21a87-4e2f-4f70-a443-ad63d4341ac2-16655668072faff6b4-2"],"custom_css":[".bls__banner-text--grid .bls__banner-text--content {box-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); border-radius: 10px; background-color: #f1f3ec;}"],"settings":{"container":"container","background_color":"","banner_type":"image","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/About_us_ledsone_banner_s.png","video_options":"local","video_url":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/about-us","hover_effect":"none","bn_design":"text_column","banner_height":"depend-image","height_dk":800,"height_tb":600,"height_mb":360,"content_box":"content_in_container","text_bellow_mobile":false,"img_position":"right","banner_width":"col-md-6","column_gap":50,"text_horizontal_position":"center","text_position":"center","text_align":"text-center","content_width":100,"content_bg_color":"","bg_opacity":100,"eb_scrolling":false,"s_text_color":"#111111","s_text_font_size":80,"s_text_font_weight":600,"text_time":10,"text_spacing":50,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":10,"reset_spacing":false}},"c3ebe82c-835b-4f82-b2f6-b38befcf6797":{"type":"banner-with-text","blocks":{"53472d49-ff77-4644-b112-81f458396685":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"txt_content":"<p>OUR QUALITY<\/p>","txt_color":"#999999","txt_fs":12,"txt_fw":500,"txt_tf":"unset","txt_mt":1,"txt_mb":5}},"template--16584037925111__c3ebe82c-835b-4f82-b2f6-b38befcf6797-16655668072faff6b4-0":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Our Product Range and Vision","heading_color":"#111111","heading_fs":40,"heading_fw":400,"heading_tf":"unset","heading_mt":0,"heading_mb":15}},"template--16584037925111__c3ebe82c-835b-4f82-b2f6-b38befcf6797-16655668072faff6b4-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"txt_content":"<p>We aim to offer our customers a variety of the latest lighting products. With more than 10 years in the industry, we know which direction to take to supply high-quality, budget-friendly products. We keep a close eye on the latest trends and put our customers’ wishes first. We believe shopping is a right, not a luxury, so we strive to deliver the best products at affordable prices, shipping them wherever you are.<br\/><br\/><\/p>","txt_color":"","txt_fs":16,"txt_fw":400,"txt_tf":"unset","txt_mt":1,"txt_mb":15}},"template--16584037925111__c3ebe82c-835b-4f82-b2f6-b38befcf6797-16655668072faff6b4-2":{"type":"buttons","disabled":true,"settings":{"btn_content":"Learn More","button_type":"link","button_link":"","button_target":false,"b_mt":0,"b_mb":15}}},"block_order":["53472d49-ff77-4644-b112-81f458396685","template--16584037925111__c3ebe82c-835b-4f82-b2f6-b38befcf6797-16655668072faff6b4-0","template--16584037925111__c3ebe82c-835b-4f82-b2f6-b38befcf6797-16655668072faff6b4-1","template--16584037925111__c3ebe82c-835b-4f82-b2f6-b38befcf6797-16655668072faff6b4-2"],"custom_css":[".bls__banner-text--grid .bls__banner-text--content {box-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); border-radius: 10px; background-color: #f1f3ec;}"],"settings":{"container":"container","background_color":"","banner_type":"image","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/About_Us_ledsone_banner_s_3.png","video_options":"local","video_url":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/about-us","hover_effect":"none","bn_design":"text_column","banner_height":"depend-image","height_dk":800,"height_tb":600,"height_mb":360,"content_box":"content_in_container","text_bellow_mobile":false,"img_position":"left","banner_width":"col-md-6","column_gap":50,"text_horizontal_position":"left","text_position":"center","text_align":"text-center","content_width":100,"content_bg_color":"","bg_opacity":100,"eb_scrolling":false,"s_text_color":"#111111","s_text_font_size":80,"s_text_font_weight":600,"text_time":10,"text_spacing":50,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"faq_nG8yNd":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"faq_6WPNd6":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"1. Where do you ship?","content":"<p>We ship across the UK and most of Europe. At checkout you’ll see available delivery options and rates based on your location.<br\/><\/p>"}},"faq_qzJyEk":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"2. How long will my order take to arrive?","content":"<p>Standard UK delivery is typically <strong>2–4 working days<\/strong>. Express options are available at checkout. European shipping times vary by country—generally <strong>5–7 working days<\/strong>.<\/p>"}},"faq_PnjbY3":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"3. Can I track my order?","content":"<p>Yes. As soon as your order is dispatched you’ll receive an email with a tracking link so you can follow its journey.<\/p>"}},"faq_MxbheM":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"4. Do you offer free shipping?","content":"<p>Orders over <strong>£25 (UK mainland)<\/strong> qualify for free standard delivery. International orders have flat-rate shipping calculated at checkout.<\/p>"}},"faq_KgnE76":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"5. What is your returns policy?","content":"<p>You can return unused, unopened items within <strong>30 days<\/strong> of receipt for a full refund or exchange. Contact us first for a returns authorisation and instructions.<\/p>"}},"faq_jaexNa":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"6. Are LEDSONE products under warranty?","content":"<p>All lighting products come with a 3 <strong>Year manufacturer’s warranty<\/strong> covering defects in materials or workmanship<br\/><\/p>"}},"faq_4iPDay":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"7. Can I get help choosing the right lighting?","content":"<p>Absolutely. Our support team and in-house designers can advise on styles, brightness levels, and energy efficiency.Email <strong>sales@ledsone.co.uk<\/strong> or call +44 <strong>02476154687<\/strong><\/p>"}},"faq_W7WMr3":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"8. Do you supply trade or bulk orders?","content":"<p>Yes—trade pricing is available for bulk purchases. Email <strong>sales@ledsone.co.uk<\/strong> your requirements.<br\/><\/p>"}},"faq_HQVnjN":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"9. How energy-efficient are your LEDs?","content":"<p>Our LEDs use up to <strong>80% less energy<\/strong> than traditional bulbs and have an average lifespan of <strong>25,000 hours<\/strong>, helping you save on electricity and replacements.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_6WPNd6","faq_qzJyEk","faq_PnjbY3","faq_MxbheM","faq_KgnE76","faq_jaexNa","faq_4iPDay","faq_W7WMr3","faq_HQVnjN"],"custom_css":[".container,.container-fluid {box-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); border-radius: 6px;}"],"name":"Faq","settings":{"heading":"Frequently Asked Questions","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"rgba(0,0,0,0)","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":12,"reset_spacing":false}},"collection_list_pdq6LW":{"type":"collection-list","blocks":{"collection_item_D7cnxm":{"type":"collection_item","settings":{"title_collection":"","collection":"all-transformers","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Power_House.png"}},"collection_item_wbqCAK":{"type":"collection_item","settings":{"title_collection":"","collection":"led-bulbs","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/LED_BULBS_E27_B22.png"}},"collection_item_HhMQLJ":{"type":"collection_item","settings":{"title_collection":"","collection":"p